[NabNova]
I was sick of trying to stream realplayer copies of my favourite radio program so wrote this to pull them down, convert to mp3, ID3 tag them and make a podcast.

[Dependencies]
 - Python
 - Mutagen: http://code.google.com/p/mutagen/
 - PyRSS2Gen: http://www.dalkescientific.com/Python/PyRSS2Gen.html

[To Do]
 - Monitor for new episodes and download them automatically without manual reruns.
